            <div class="who-heading">Who are Aviation Enthusiasts?</div>
            <div class="who-info">
                <p>Aviation Enthusiasts are people who have a passion for aviation and you can detect one by seeing what their reaction or responses are when you talk about aviation with them or when they see planes, go to an airport, etc...</p>
                <p>Aviation Enthusiasts, are also refered to as, "AvGeeks." AvGeeks usually go to anything related with aviation and you might find them correcting non AvGeeks when they talk about aviation.</p>
                <p>AvGeeks also participate in many airshows or such events and they might have a flight simulator, in which they can simulate flying a real aeroplane. There are some who would build a remote controlled aeroplane and fly it around. Finally, some AvGeeks keep a collection of items like propellers hanging on the wall, or keychains, etc...</p>
                <p>AvGeeks are found in many places especially on the internet (YouTube, Instagram...). If you are intersted to become an AvGeek or increase your knowledge about them, then you can follow some channles on those Platforms. It will take time, but as you continue your journey, you will enjoy it and learn as you enjoy. </p>
