                <ul>
                    <li>They detect almost any plane they see in front of them.</li>
                    <li>They love and enjoy it while takeoff and landing.</li>
                    <li>They have a flight simulator and try to get any games related to avaition. Including Phone, PC...</li>
                    <li>They try to build a small model of a specific plane that they can attempt to fly.</li>
                    <li>They try and go to the cockpit, trying to see the systems and all in front of their eyes.</li>
                    <li>Their instagram is full of Aviation related stuff.</li>
                    <li>They are concerned of what plane they are/will be flying on, unlike their friends who don't care as much.</li>
                    <li>They are either in Team Airbus or Team Boeing.</li>
                    <li>When their is a plane flying they try to identify which one it is.</li>
                    <li>They go to events related to avaition such as airshows and introductons to new models of planes.</li>
